---
---

<section class="system-overview" id="markethink-system" aria-label="How Markethink works">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="system-cards animate-stagger">
      <article class="system-card system-card-chat">
        <div class="system-visual" aria-hidden="true">
          <div class="visual-glow"></div>
          <div class="chat-thread chat-thread-left">
            <div class="message message-user user-one">
              <span class="avatar avatar-warm"></span>
              <div>
                <strong>Team</strong>
                <p>@Markethink we need next week’s campaign plan</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="message message-user user-two">
              <span class="avatar avatar-soft"></span>
              <div>
                <strong>Founder</strong>
                <p>include the lead follow-up angle too</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="message message-system">
              <span class="markethink-avatar">M</span>
              <div>
                <strong>Markethink <em>system</em></strong>
                <p>Here you go — ready for review.</p>
                <span class="file-pill">campaign-plan.pdf</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="system-copy">
          <p>Dashboard</p>
          <h2>Real marketing output, not just chat.</h2>
          <span>Campaigns, content, approvals, leads, assets, and next steps stay visible in one organized place instead of getting buried across chats and files.</span>
        </div>
      </article>

      <article class="system-card system-card-tools">
        <div class="system-visual" aria-hidden="true">
          <div class="visual-glow"></div>
          <div class="tool-orbit">
            <span class="tool-card tool-ads">Ads</span>
            <span class="tool-card tool-crm">CRM</span>
            <span class="tool-card tool-web">Web</span>
            <span class="tool-card tool-social">Social</span>
            <span class="tool-card tool-email">Email</span>
            <span class="tool-card tool-search">Search</span>
            <div class="tool-center">
              <span>M</span>
              <small>one message</small>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="system-copy">
          <p>24/7 Operator</p>
          <h2>One message moves the system.</h2>
          <span>Your trained operator learns the business, remembers approvals, and prepares the next piece of work so your team is not restarting from zero every week.</span>
        </div>
      </article>

      <article class="system-card system-card-memory">
        <div class="system-visual" aria-hidden="true">
          <div class="visual-glow"></div>
          <div class="chat-thread chat-thread-right">
            <div class="message message-user user-three">
              <span class="avatar avatar-charcoal"></span>
              <div>
                <strong>Operator</strong>
                <p>@Markethink any updates?</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="message message-system compact-card">
              <span class="markethink-avatar">M</span>
              <div>
                <strong>Markethink <em>system</em></strong>
                <p>Lead list is ready. Follow-up angle is stronger now.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="message message-system compact-card second-response">
              <span class="markethink-avatar">M</span>
              <div>
                <strong>Markethink <em>system</em></strong>
                <p>I kept the approval from last week.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="system-copy">
          <p>Expert Team</p>
          <h2>Never restart from zero.</h2>
          <span>Strategy, copy, design, web, lead research, and follow-up support work behind the system so Markethink delivers judgment, not just output.</span>
        </div>
      </article>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .system-overview {
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    padding: clamp(4.5rem, 7vw, 7.5rem) 0 2rem;
    background: #f5f5f1;
    color: #0f1213;
  }

  .system-overview::before {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background:
      radial-gradient(circle at 16% 10%, rgba(105, 210, 84, 0.12), transparent 29rem),
      radial-gradient(circle at 82% 28%, rgba(237, 244, 234, 0.95), transparent 34rem);
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .system-overview .container {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .system-cards {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
    gap: clamp(1rem, 2vw, 1.4rem);
  }

  .system-card {
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    min-height: 35rem;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    border: 1px solid rgba(15, 18, 19, 0.08);
    border-radius: 2.15rem;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 252, 0.9);
    box-shadow: 0 24px 80px rgba(15, 18, 19, 0.09);
  }

  .system-visual {
    position: relative;
    min-height: 19rem;
    overflow: hidden;
    background:
      linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(15, 18, 19, 0.92) 0%, rgba(15, 18, 19, 0.92) 36%, rgba(245, 245, 241, 0.98) 36%, rgba(245, 245, 241, 0.98) 100%);
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(15, 18, 19, 0.06);
  }

  .visual-glow {
    position: absolute;
    inset: -18% -8% auto -8%;
    height: 14rem;
    background: radial-gradient(circle at 50% 45%, rgba(105, 210, 84, 0.36), rgba(237, 244, 234, 0.62) 34%, transparent 72%);
    filter: blur(12px);
    opacity: 0.95;
  }

  .chat-thread {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 1.3rem clamp(1rem, 2vw, 1.45rem) auto;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.74rem;
  }

  .message {
    position: relative;
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 0.62rem;
    border-radius: 1.2rem;
    color: #0f1213;
  }

  .message strong {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.38rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.16rem;
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    font-weight: 850;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  }

  .message strong em {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    height: 1rem;
    padding: 0 0.34rem;
    border-radius: 999px;
    background: rgba(105, 210, 84, 0.18);
    color: #0f1213;
    font-size: 0.48rem;
    font-style: normal;
    font-weight: 850;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .message p {
    margin: 0;
    color: #303333;
    font-size: clamp(0.72rem, 0.9vw, 0.86rem);
    line-height: 1.32;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  }

  .message-user {
    width: min(20rem, 92%);
    padding: 0.15rem 0.2rem;
    color: #f5f5f1;
  }

  .message-user strong,
  .message-user p {
    color: #f5f5f1;
  }

  .message-user p {
    opacity: 0.94;
  }

  .message-system {
    width: min(22rem, 96%);
    margin-top: 0.15rem;
    padding: 0.86rem 0.9rem;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 252, 0.82);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 252, 0.75);
    box-shadow: 0 18px 58px rgba(15, 18, 19, 0.18), 0 0 48px rgba(105, 210, 84, 0.16);
    backdrop-filter: blur(16px);
    -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(16px);
  }

  .chat-thread-left .message-system {
    animation: answer-float 7s ease-in-out infinite;
  }

  .chat-thread-right .message-system {
    width: min(21rem, 94%);
    animation: answer-float 7.8s ease-in-out infinite;
  }

  .second-response {
    align-self: flex-end;
    animation-delay: -2.4s;
  }

  .avatar,
  .markethink-avatar {
    flex: 0 0 auto;
    width: 1.85rem;
    height: 1.85rem;
    border-radius: 50%;
  }

  .avatar-warm {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f5f5f1, #b4b6b6);
  }

  .avatar-soft {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #edf4ea, #69d254);
  }

  .avatar-charcoal {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #686b6c, #0f1213);
    border: 1px solid rgba(245, 245, 241, 0.55);
  }

  .markethink-avatar {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    border-radius: 0.68rem;
    background: #0f1213;
    color: #69d254;
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 1.15rem;
    line-height: 1;
    box-shadow: 0 10px 24px rgba(15, 18, 19, 0.18);
  }

  .file-pill {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    margin-top: 0.55rem;
    padding: 0.34rem 0.62rem;
    border-radius: 999px;
    background: #69d254;
    color: #0f1213;
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    font-weight: 850;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
  }

  .tool-orbit {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    display: grid;
    place-items: center;
    perspective: 900px;
  }

  .tool-orbit::before,
  .tool-orbit::after {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    width: 16rem;
    height: 16rem;
    border-radius: 50%;
    border: 1px dashed rgba(105, 210, 84, 0.28);
    animation: orbit-spin 18s linear infinite;
  }

  .tool-orbit::after {
    width: 11.5rem;
    height: 11.5rem;
    border-color: rgba(245, 245, 241, 0.32);
    animation-duration: 12s;
    animation-direction: reverse;
  }

  .tool-card {
    position: absolute;
    display: grid;
    place-items: center;
    width: 4.5rem;
    height: 4.5rem;
    border-radius: 1.05rem;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 252, 0.88);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 252, 0.85);
    box-shadow: 0 18px 54px rgba(15, 18, 19, 0.18);
    color: #0f1213;
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    font-weight: 880;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    transform: rotate(var(--angle)) translateX(7.2rem) rotate(calc(var(--angle) * -1));
    animation: tool-breathe 8s ease-in-out infinite;
  }

  .tool-ads { --angle: -82deg; animation-delay: -0.4s; }
  .tool-crm { --angle: -22deg; animation-delay: -1.7s; }
  .tool-web { --angle: 42deg; animation-delay: -3.1s; }
  .tool-social { --angle: 102deg; animation-delay: -4.5s; }
  .tool-email { --angle: 164deg; animation-delay: -5.8s; }
  .tool-search { --angle: 218deg; animation-delay: -6.9s; }

  .tool-center {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
    display: grid;
    place-items: center;
    width: 6.25rem;
    height: 6.25rem;
    border-radius: 1.45rem;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 252, 0.94);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 252, 0.9);
    box-shadow: 0 22px 70px rgba(15, 18, 19, 0.2), 0 0 42px rgba(105, 210, 84, 0.18);
  }

  .tool-center span {
    color: #0f1213;
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 2.55rem;
    line-height: 0.84;
  }

  .tool-center small {
    margin-top: -0.8rem;
    color: #686b6c;
    font-size: 0.58rem;
    font-weight: 850;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .system-copy {
    display: flex;
    flex: 1;
    flex-direction: column;
    padding: clamp(1.35rem, 2vw, 1.8rem);
  }

  .system-copy > p {
    width: max-content;
    margin-bottom: 1.05rem;
    padding: 0.38rem 0.72rem;
    border: 1px solid rgba(105, 210, 84, 0.34);
    border-radius: 999px;
    color: #0f1213;
    background: rgba(237, 244, 234, 0.86);
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    font-weight: 820;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .system-copy h2 {
    max-width: 21rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: #0f1213;
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: clamp(2.2rem, 3vw, 3.25rem);
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 0.93;
    letter-spacing: -0.052em;
  }

  .system-copy span {
    display: block;
    margin-top: auto;
    color: #686b6c;
    font-size: 0.98rem;
    line-height: 1.65;
  }

  @keyframes answer-float {
    0%, 100% { transform: translate3d(0, 0, 0); }
    50% { transform: translate3d(0.35rem, -0.45rem, 0); }
  }

  @keyframes orbit-spin {
    from { transform: rotate(0deg); }
    to { transform: rotate(360deg); }
  }

  @keyframes tool-breathe {
    0%, 100% { filter: saturate(0.96); opacity: 0.82; }
    50% { filter: saturate(1.08); opacity: 1; }
  }

  @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
    .chat-thread-left .message-system,
    .chat-thread-right .message-system,
    .tool-orbit::before,
    .tool-orbit::after,
    .tool-card {
      animation: none;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 1040px) {
    .system-cards {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .system-card {
      min-height: auto;
    }

    .system-copy span {
      margin-top: 0.5rem;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 560px) {
    .system-overview {
      padding-top: 4rem;
    }

    .system-card {
      border-radius: 1.35rem;
    }

    .system-visual {
      min-height: 16.75rem;
    }

    .system-copy h2 {
      font-size: clamp(2.05rem, 10vw, 2.7rem);
    }

    .message p {
      font-size: 0.7rem;
    }

    .message-system {
      padding: 0.76rem;
    }

    .tool-card {
      width: 3.65rem;
      height: 3.65rem;
      transform: rotate(var(--angle)) translateX(5.6rem) rotate(calc(var(--angle) * -1));
      font-size: 0.62rem;
    }

    .tool-center {
      width: 5.2rem;
      height: 5.2rem;
    }
  }
</style>
